            "text": "We‚Äôve been familiar with Apocalypse Jeep builds for some time as well as other 6x6 conversions for trucks and off-road rigs. However, the public at large was just introduced to the concept in a big way when NBA Star Luka Doncic arrived for a game recently behind the wheel of an ",
