            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The next shocking revelation came when the media announced the Jeep probably set the basketball player back a healthy $200,000. While we agree that‚Äôs a substantial amount of money, we also know these sorts of aftermarket builds don‚Äôt come cheap.",
            "type": "text",
